data.description: Pond front oasis in beautiful Freeport!  Less than 30 minutes to the sugar white sand beaches of 30a!  Custom home built in 2020 by John Cunningham with numerous upgrades.  Enter through the stunning cedar trimmed front porch and experience an open floor plan featuring 3 beds and 2 baths plus a private office with french doors for extra privacy.  The master features an oversize walk-in closet with built-in drawers, tray ceilings, quartz counters, and a double-head walk-in shower.  The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, quartz counters and an under-mounted sink.  Plenty of storage space.  Laundry room also has a separate sink. Enjoy your morning coffee or an afternoon wine on your screened-in porch overlooking the pond.  *Buyer to verify all info/dimensions.
